Search the entire repository for files named exactly `Dockerfile` or matching `Dockerfile.*` (e.g., `Dockerfile.prod`, `Dockerfile.dev`). Also check `docker-compose.yml` and `docker-compose.*.yml` files for inline `build.dockerfile` references that point to additional Dockerfiles. Process every Dockerfile found.

